           </a>
          </div>
         </div>
        </div>
        <div class="view-content">
         <div class="chapter">
          <h3>
           <a href="/handbook/academic-appointments">
            Academic Appointments
           </a>
          </h3>
          <p>
           Policies and resources for the life cycle of all academic appointees - from signing on to signing off.
          </p>
         </div>
         <div class="chapter">
          <h3>
           <a href="/handbook/research">
            Research
           </a>
          </h3>
          <p>
           Learn about the resources, policies, and facilities available at the University to help you develop your research.
          </p>
         </div>
         <div class="chapter">
          <h3>
           <a href="/handbook/teaching">
            Teaching
           </a>
          </h3>
          <p>
           Resources, policies, and programs for all academics at the University. Develop your pedagogy, reach all learners, and engage the campus.
          </p>
         </div>
         <div class="chapter">
          <h3>
           <a href="/handbook/life">
            Life
           </a>
          </h3>
          <p>
           Resources, programs, and assistance for academics and their families. Learn what the University has to offer.
          </p>
         </div>
        </div>
       </div>
      </div>
